# Portent iOS

Bundle ID: `com.notitial.portent`. Swift 6, SwiftUI, MVVM, @Observable, URLSession. **Minimum:** iOS 18. **visionOS:** Not supported. **macOS:** Catalyst only (not day-one).

## Navigation

- Root: Adaptive TabView (bottom tabs on iPhone, sidebar on iPad)
- Per-tab: NavigationStack + NavigationDestination

## Tabs (4)

Dashboard | Calendar | Services | Search

## State

Sealed UiState: Loading | Success | Error | Refreshing(staleData). Refreshing for pull-to-refresh. @Observable for ViewModel observation.

## Feature Structure

```
Features/<Name>/
  Data/       — Service impl, DTOs
  Domain/     — Service protocol, UseCase (optional)
  Presentation/ — ViewModel, View, State
```

## Mono Repo

Platform code lives here; shared docs in `portent/docs/`, `portent/core/`. See `docs/agents/agent-ios.md`.
